<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fear-v">fear <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /fɪə(r)/    美 /fɪr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>害怕；畏惧：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He fears nothing.
他什么都不怕。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My daughter <strong>fears to</strong> speak in public.
我女儿害怕在公共场合讲话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>fears walking</strong> alone at night.
她不敢一个人在夜间行走。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>担心：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>feared for</strong> her safety.
他们为她的安全担忧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The woman has been missing for three days and police are beginning to <strong>fear the worst</strong> (= think that she is dead).
这名妇女已经失踪3天了，警方担心发生了最坏的事情。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I really <strong>feared</strong> (<strong>that</strong>) I might miss the train.
我真担心自己可能赶不上火车了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>fearful /'fɪəfl/ adj <br />
fearless /'fɪələs/ adj   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>He got to the station early, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ fear of missing his train.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>